branchCategory.name: Rodless Cylinder, MY3*, Mechanically Jointed - Basic Type
branchCategory.description: <p>The MY3* Rodless Cylinders have a one-piece carriage and piston that runs its entire stroke length housed with an inner seal belt to maintain air pressure combined with an outer dust seal band to protect from contaminants. This design offers a compact footprint compared to rod-style cylinders and features a low profile. It is available with rubber bumpers, air cushions or external shock absorbers as well as a stroke adjuster unit.</p>
